ens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"This provider should be integrated as a ","type":"text"},{"code":"AllControlItemComponentTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" implementation inside ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" so as to provide","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" implementation to use.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Custom themes can use subclass of ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" and apply the provider they need.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It implements also the protocol ","type":"text"},{"code":"ControlItemComponentTokens","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" so as to expose the component tokens for control-item-layout-basded components through any ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Such components tokens are defined with raw and semantic tokens of sizes (from ","type":"text"},{"code":"SizeSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"),","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"colors (from ","type":"text"},{"code":"AllColorSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":")  and spaces (from ","type":"text"},{"code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":")?","type":"text"}],"relationshipsSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDS\/documentation\/OUDS\/AllControlItemComponentTokensProvider","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/19OUDSTokensComponent011ControlItemB6TokensP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/s8CopyableP","doc:\/\/OUDS\/documentation\/OUDS\/Token